com.brightcove.player.event

Class EventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brightcove.player.event.EventType

  • public final class EventType
extends java.lang.Object
    Maintains a list of Event types that the system is aware of. New events introduced to the system should be located here. However, because we're really just passing around strings, it's fully possible for users to create and use their own events.
